    ns1:numberOfCredits 4.5 ;
    ns1:otherInformation """The course will be imparted intensively during half a semester (8 weeks)
Several innovative teaching methodologies are implemented in this course to motivate and reinforce learning:
- Learning by doing: through in-class exercises.
- Gamification in the classroom: through knowledge competitions using the Wooclap tool.
- Project-based learning: through the completion of practical assignments."""@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Junio"@es ;
    ns1:periodStartingMonth "Febrero"@es ;
    ns1:teachingPeriod "2025-26" ;
    ns1:teachingPeriodMonths "Febrero-Junio"@es ;
    ns1:totalHours "46 horas"@es ;
    schema:activitiesWorkload "100%"@es ;
    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000901/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description "The amount of available data in most scientific areas has grown dramatically during the last few years. However, this increment did not have a parallel impact on the knowledge available for decision-making. There is a need for automated models to manage such data, considering that human beings will never directly use most of it. The course Information Retrieval, Extraction, and Integration focuses on the necessary methods and tools to extract information and models to efficiently retrieve data for further integration. These are critical tasks to provide relevant information for decision making, whose complexity increases with the amount of data available. As application areas, we focus mainly on biomedicine due to the complexity and the specific requirements."@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/miguel.garcia.remesal%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/david.perez.rey%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/mdelcarmen.suarezdefigueroa%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/miguel.garcia.remesal%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/raul.alonso%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/victormanuel.maojo%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "Information Retrieval, Extraction And Integration"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000901/2025-26/CECD01> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CECD01" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Conocer los procesos de captura, extracción, manipulación y conversión de datos en diferentes entornos/ To know the processes of data capture, extraction, handling and transformation in different environments."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000901/2025-26/CG06> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG06" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Especificación y realización de tareas informáticas complejas, poco definidas o no familiares/ To specify and complete informatics tasks that are complex, incompletely defined, or unfamiliar."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000901/2025-26/CG07> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG07" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Aplicación de los últimos o más novedosos métodos para resolver problemas que, posiblemente, involucren a otras disciplinas/ To apply state"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000901/2025-26/CG09> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG09" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Integración del conocimiento de distintos campos de estudio/ To apply and integrate knowledge and understanding of other informatics disciplines in support of study in their own specialist area(s)."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000901/2025-26/CG14> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG14" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Capacidad de trabajar y comunicarse también en contextos internacionales/ To communicate effectively, both verbally and through a variety of communications media, to a variety of different audiences, and preferably also in a second language."@es .

